topic.title: "my new site" bug
topic.body:
I have a public key 1C8UBEHWorexK8pk1mLqXSiTv3SFvvz8eY for a site ( called "my new site" ) , when i try to delete it from the zeronet menu , it says it is my site , but when I try to delete from windows explorer into "data" , I can't find it , because I have already delete it from windows explorer into "data".
